news.title: Anthurium Developers and GKW to jointly develop 37 acre land parcel in Mumbai’s Bhandup
news.para: This land parcel will have a development potential of around 3.6 million sq ft. It will be a mixed-use development with residential, commercial and retail components.

news.title: Spain's Inmocemento to make market debut valued at $2.1 billion
news.para: The company, which has 454.9 million shares, set a reference share price of 4.25 euros for its listing, according to a late Thursday filing to Spain's stock market regulator.

news.title: US's mortgage rates rises to 6.79% in November 2024
news.para: The average rate on the popular 30-year fixed-rate mortgage climbed to 6.79%, the highest level since July, from 6.72% last week, mortgage finance agency Freddie Mac said on Thursday.

news.title: Mysuru development body's 50:50 site-sharing scheme sparks debate
news.para: Some members urged Mysuru DC G Lakshikanth Reddy, who is the MUDA chairman, to fully cancel the allotment of sites under the scheme between 2020 and 2024, calling them unlawful and to restore the credibility of the urban development body.

news.title: Chandigarh: Only 20% of homes apply for mandatory rooftop solar installation
news.para: The UT estate office on Sept 6 had issued resumption notices to more than 4,000 homeowners having a plot size of 500 sq yard or more for not installing the rooftop solar plants.

news.title: Hyderabad: CCS takes over 2-BHK housing allotment fraud case
news.para: Earlier, a case was registered at the Borabanda police station and it revolves around Gondri Narasimha Raju, who claimed close ties with Jubilee Hills MLA Maganti Gopinath to convince a victim to pay for a promised 2-BHK flat.

news.title: Calcutta HC orders probe into alleged PMAY fund fraud in Canning
news.para: "It's a deliberate fraud," Justice Kapur observed after perusing the report by the state, which submitted that funds for the five beneficiaries were deposited in the bank accounts of others.

news.title: Goa TCP department approves 52 zone change applications covering 1.4 lakh sq meter
news.para: The total area that is being converted based on the 52 applications is 1.4 lakh sqm, which includes 68,399sqm at Sarvona-Bicholim, 20,000 sqm at Arambol-Pernem and 9,215 sqm at Corgao-Pernem.

news.title: Embassy REIT appoints Ritwik Bhattacharjee as interim CEO
news.para: The moves comes after Sebi's recent order cum show cause notice directing the suspension of Aravind Maiya as CEO of Embassy REIT.

news.title: Propsoch raises $500,000 in pre-seed funding led by Godrej and Vakil family offices
news.para: The funds will be used for market expansion efforts in Mumbai and Pune and scaling up its operations in Bengaluru.

news.title: GBA urges Goa RERA to deregister Bhutani Infra's project in Sancoale
news.para: In a letter to the Real Estate Regulatory Authority (RERA), Goa, the organisation has called for immediate action against the project registered under the name of Acqua Eden.

news.title: Ghaziabad development body auctions 23 plots, earns revenue of Rs 58 crore
news.para: Two plots under the commercial category and three residential ones were auctioned at the Indirapuram housing scheme, fetching Rs 37.9 crore," said Pradeep Singh, additional secretary at GDA.

news.title: HC issues notice to ED and Ireo Group's MD over alleged bail violations in property transfers
news.para: Ireo Group's MD has been facing a money-laundering case in relation to a cheating case registered against him in Pinjore, Panchkula district, for cheating buyers of a housing project allegedly launched by him.

news.title: Brookfield India REIT's net operating income up 40% to Rs 486 crore in Q2 FY25
news.para: The board of directors of Brookprop Management Services Pvt Ltd, the manager of Brookfield India Real Estate Trust, approved the issuance of units of Brookfield India REIT through an institutional placement of units not exceeding Rs 3,500 crore in one or more placement.

news.title: Brigade Group to jointly develop one million sq ft residential project in Chennai
news.para: The project, located in West Chennai will be developed as part of a 1.5 million sq ft mixed-use development and will have a gross development value (GDV) of about Rs 800 crore.

news.title: Nagpur: Couple booked for duping three people of Rs 3.7 crore in land deal fraud
news.para: According to police, Anand and Sarda are directors in a real estate company and own an office in Nawanakasha. The complainant, Asim Nawed Issararulha, a resident of Gittikhadan, came in contact with the accused in 2022.

news.title: Retail space leasing in malls, main high streets falls 1% to 1.63 million sq ft during Jul-Sep 2024: Report
news.para: Real estate consultant Cushman & Wakefield on Thursday released its Q3-2024 'Retail Market Beat' report, which highlighted a sustained momentum across India's main streets, leading retail growth across the top 8 cities.

news.title: Bengaluru to add 175 km of new metro lines by 2026: Karnataka deputy CM
news.para: Addressing a press conference after inspecting the newly extended line from Nagasandra to Madavara on Tumkur Road, he said, "Thirty kilometers of new metro lines will be added by 2025, and 175 km of new metro lines will be operational by 2026."

news.title: Bajaj Electricals' net profit declines 59.28% in Q2 FY25
news.para: Bajaj Electricals' net consolidated total income stood at Rs 1,133.52 crore in Q2 FY25 a growth of 0.88 per cent from Rs 1,123.63 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.
